T1  - Unfiltered Market Access and Liquidity: Evidence from the SEC Rule 15c3-5
AU  - Chakrabarty, Bidisha
AU  - Jain, Pankaj K.
AU  - Shkilko, Andriy
AU  - Sokolov, Konstantin
Y1  - 2020/05/20
